  const safeSlug = escapeHtml(slug); // escapeHtml from S002
  return renderPage(`Report: ${safeSlug}`, `
    <h1>${safeSlug}</h1>
    <p>Report coming soon.</p>
    <p><a href="/">← Back to product list</a></p>
  `);
}
```

Uses `renderPage()` and `escapeHtml()` helpers established in S002.

---

### 7. 404 page HTML

```ts
