  return renderPage("Product not found", `
    <h1>Product not found</h1>
    <p>The requested product could not be found.</p>
    <p><a href="/">← Back to product list</a></p>
  `);
}
```

The 404 page uses the same `renderPage()` HTML shell for consistent styling.

