- "notion-so" → true  
- "a" → true
- "" → false
- "../etc/passwd" → false
- "foo/bar" → false
- ".hidden" → false
- "UPPERCASE" → false
- "a".repeat(200) → false (length check)
```

#### c) Slug routing integration tests (HTTP-level)
Using the same pattern as S001/S002 tests: create a temp `ProductDirectory`, start server on port 0, make HTTP requests.

**Setup:**
